The paper deals with knowledge graph embeddings, which are a popular topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses network effects and similarity in networks, which are relevant to social networks and network science (cs.SI). The paper proposes a method to improve link prediction in knowledge graphs, which is a task in information retrieval (cs.IR) and databases (cs.DB).
